  "name": "Nagaraja COU1 — Orthopedic tibial tray finite element credibility assessment (MRL 3)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for a finite element (FE) model predicting primary stability and micromotion of a cementless tibial tray under physiological loading. COU1 evaluates whether the computational model can predict relative micromotional displacement at the bone-implant interface for a Class II orthopedic device at Model Risk Level 3. All 13 credibility factors are fully assessed; achieved levels meet or exceed required levels at MRL 3. Decision: Accepted.",
