    "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/cou/nagaraja-cou1-tibial-tray",
    "intendedUse": "Use FE analysis to predict peak micromotion (microns) at five bone-implant interface regions under three loading scenarios (level gait, stair ascent, stair descent) for a cementless tibial tray. Results used to rank design variants relative to a 150-micron osseointegration threshold. Uncertainty quantification via Latin Hypercube Sampling on material and geometric inputs.",
